  m_text: "The world outside is still \u2014 no buzzing alarms, no rush. Soft sunlight
    spills across Alex\u2019s desk, lighting up notebooks and half\u2011finished
    plans. A cup of coffee sends gentle wisps of steam into the air. For a moment,
    there\u2019s peace \u2014 just Alex, her thoughts, and the steady hum of a new
    day waiting to unfold"
