  m_text: "The days blur into motion \u2014 notebooks opening, pens scribbling, laughter
    echoing in hallways. Morning coffee turns into late\u2011night reviews, quick
    meals, and quiet walks home under orange streetlights. Between stress and smiles,
    Alex keeps moving \u2014 learning, adjusting, and growing in ways she barely
    notices. Just another day, another step forward"
